0893   04F5 FD 0A ED 04   jmp [io_jmp + al]
0894   04F9             ; bit7 is the Divisor Latch Access Bit (DLAB). It must be set high (logic 1) to access the Divisor Latches
0895   04F9             ; of the Baud Generator during a Read or Write operation. It must be set low (logic 0) to access the Receiver
